.IP \[bu] 2
start - Start index of the subset of the vertex buffer to draw
.IP \[bu] 2
end - One past the last index of the subset of the vertex buffer to draw
.IP \[bu] 2
type - A member of the ALLEGRO_PRIM_TYPE(3) enumeration, specifying what
